          </description>
          <description>
            <para>
              <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/Controls/common-control-versions">Version 6.00 and later</a>. The group can be collapsed.</para>
          </description>
        </item>
        <item>
          <description>
            <list type="bullet">
              <item>
                <description>
